{"tid":13173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔領停機坪踢毽selfie 強國客抗議航班延誤","createTime":"2016-11-30T02:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T03:53:58.000Z","uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd8bed0b8cfeed36ff18bc85e36ebee7cc17e1f","tid":13173,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161129/large/1480420966_3cec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161129%2Flarge%2F1480420966_3cec.jpg&h=75b308e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日內地媒體報道，前日凌晨祥鵬航空從雲南西雙版納嘎灑國際機場飛往昆明、編號為8L9917的客機，因機長不滿被「插隊」要延遲起飛，竟呼籲乘客下機到停機坪處「抗議」，給機場施壓，有乘客更踢毽自拍，最終延遲了3小時起飛。<br />\n<br />\n當日「抗議」活動進行了不久，機場與航空公司達成了協議，並派機長前去勸導乘客返回機上。由於機長的態度反覆，原本支持機長的乘客感到不快，表示：「我們是聽你的話才下來的，你讓我們下來我們就下來，讓我們走我們就走」，又表示他們為了「支持機長」，決定「留下不走」，其中12人當場去辦理終止行程的手續。<br />\n經過多番擾攘，一個多小時之後，很多乘客仍不願意登機，最終有12人免費改簽，其他人飛往昆明。約凌晨3時成功起飛，到達昆明已凌晨4時，祥鵬航空表示會對相關責任人進行嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做乜鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1546a8237aa1ab6b485e15ab11ba64655a74ee3","tid":13173,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:29:14.000Z","msg":"算唔算比機長過左一棟"},{"pid":"8e9784f824e7ce9044048806b42e291efec383d0","tid":13173,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"點解唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844dd2ba6804d034f0c5e07c3038a5816db6e35f","tid":13173,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:40:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蝗國既野唔明係正常"},{"pid":"511368c598d6a613a5c10711c466d7504c4be911","tid":13173,"uid":28863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:44:32.000Z","msg":"踢毽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴撚線"},{"pid":"026bbcd834592cae8c5dca94495ceb8b8402570f","tid":13173,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"個機長做乜唔飛左先，然後再撞控制塔。<br />\n<br />\n咁既 EQ 都搾飛機，痴撚線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2484cc605006fc6578d91e96eb49be4d73f767","tid":13173,"uid":36126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:53:58.000Z","msg":"不能理解既邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}